name: The Anomaly - Croissant
description:
Piece Of Cake collectible Esoteric cards starring Goddesses and Daemons.

As you walk in the Tezos Blockchain, you suddenly smell something tasty. It brings you back memories :
You see yourself as a child, during a sunny but cold sunday morning. Your mom is preparing hot chocolate, dad is back home and is holding a paper bag from the pastry shop.

This smell is familiar, you look above and you literally see croissants falling from a shiny ring in the sky. You realize that they vanish above your head. After a while, you hear something soft touching the ground behind you. It seems that a croissant was able to reach the ground intact.

You decide to inspect it :

ITEM : CROISSANT
ORIGIN : ANOMALY
QUANTITY AVAILABLE : 10

Would you like to put it in INVENTORY ?
